(Submitted photo: CoStar) Eatery, offices planned for $4.1M North Loop building By: Karlee Weinmann September 28, 2015 1:58 pm 0 Restaurateur Paul Dzubnar, who runs Green Mill Restaurants, paid $4.1 million for a three-floor office building in the trendy North Loop section of Minneapolis.
